<div class="info-box">
  <h4>Which Immersion Device to Choose</h4>
  <p>
    <strong>Prioritize consistency and ease:</strong> Clever Dripper<br />
    <strong>Want rich, heavy-bodied coffee:</strong> French Press<br />
    <strong>Enjoy experimenting and variety:</strong> AeroPress<br />
    <strong>Want a visual experience and delicate clarity:</strong> Siphon<br /><br />
    All of these produce outstanding cups with the right approach. Understand each device's character, then choose based on what suits the bean and the moment.
  </p>
</div>

